<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>가약 - Custom Wedding</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/product_info_page.css">
</head>
<body>

<!-- 슬라이드 컨테이너 -->
<div class="scroll-container">

    <!-- 상단 메뉴 섹션 -->
    <section class="product_info_page-section1">
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="product_list_page">상품</a>
            <a href="book_page">예약</a>
            <a href="inquiry">문의</a>
            <a href="confirm_reservation">확인</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 제품 정보 섹션 -->
    <div class="product_info_page-section2">
        <div class="product_info_page-section2-sector1">
            <img id="product-main-image" src="" alt="제품 이미지">
        </div>
        <div class="product_info_page-section2-sector2">
            <h2 id="product-name">제품명</h2>
            <p id="product-code" class="product_info_page-section2-sector2-product-code">제품 코드</p>
            <div id="product-description" class="product_info_page-section2-sector2-product-description-box">
                제품 설명이 여기에 표시됩니다.
            </div>
            
            <div class="dropdown-menu">
                <span class="dropdown-label">색상</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="custom-color-options">
                <label class="custom-radio">
                    <input type="radio" name="custom-color" value="black">
                    <span class="checkmark checkmark-black"></span> 검은색
                </label>
                <label class="custom-radio">
                    <input type="radio" name="custom-color" value="white">
                    <span class="checkmark checkmark-white"></span> 흰색
                </label>
            </div>

            <div class="custom-buttons">
                <button class="custom-inquire-button">서랍 넣기</button>
                <button class="custom-cart-button">달력 확인</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="product-info">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-header">
                        <span>제품 크기</span>
                        <button class="toggle-button">+</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <p>제품 크기에 대한 상세 설명이 여기에 들어갑니다. 예: 100cm x 50cm x 30cm</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-header">
                        <span>유의사항</span>
                        <button class="toggle-button">+</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <p>유의사항에 대한 상세 설명이 여기에 들어갑니다. 예: 직사광선을 피하고 건조한 곳에 보관하세요.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 슬라이더 섹션 -->
    <section class="product_info_page-section3">
        <div class="slider-container">
            <div class="slider" id="product-slider">
                <!-- 슬라이더 이미지 동적 로드 -->
            </div>
            <div class="pagination"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 본품 구성 섹션 -->
    <section class="product_info_page-section35">
        <div>
            <h2>본품 구성</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content-product-grid" id="product-supplements">
            <!-- 본품 구성 동적 로드 -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 추천 상품 섹션 -->
    <div class="product_info_page-section4">
        <h2>추천 상품</h2>
        <div class="product-grid2" id="recommended-products">
            <!-- 추천 상품 동적 로드 -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 푸터 섹션 -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-big-container">
            <div class="footer-container">
                <div class="footer-info">
                    <div class="footer-logo">
                        <img src="/image/logo.png" alt="회사 로고">
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-company">
                        <h4>회사</h4>
                        <p>사업자 주소 | 인천부평구 부개동 55-555</p>
                        <p>사업자 등록 번호 | 00000-0000-0000-0000</p>
                        <p>대표 전화번호 | (010) 9931 1981</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-service">
                        <h4>고객 서비스</h4>
                        <p><a href="/faq">자주 묻는 질문(FAQ)</a></p>
                        <p><a href="/support">고객 지원/고객 문의</a></p>
                        <p><a href="/returns">반품 및 환불 정책</a></p>
                        <p><a href="/contact">영업팀과 문의</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <div class="footer-icons">
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank">
                        <img src="/image/instagram.png" alt="Instagram 아이콘">
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.kakaotalk.com" target="_blank">
                        <img src="/image/kakaotalk.png" alt="KakaoTalk 아이콘">
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-policy">
                    <p>
                        <a href="/privacy-policy">개인정보 처리방침</a> |
                        <a href="/terms-of-service">사이트 이용약관</a> |
                        <a href="/cookie-policy">쿠키 정책</a> |
                        <a href="/company-info">사업자 정보</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-signature">
                    <img src="/image/kayak.png" alt="가약 이미지">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</div>

<!-- JavaScript 연결 -->
<script src="/js/product_info_page.js"></script>

</body>
</html>